{"tid":1789072,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"蘋果財經：澳門搞金融 香港開賭場","createTime":"2019-12-19T07:46:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T07:46:21.000Z","uid":228995,"like":325,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"f0805ed2bda3c442f639b85df724e909b1e5c432","tid":1789072,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T07:46:19.000Z","msg":"//<br />\n在澳門回歸中國20周年之際，中央似乎會給澳門「送大禮」，包括成立人民幣結算平台，發行人民幣債券等，想跟香港搶食。<br />\n<br />\n其實，這不是新聞。早在今年4月，中央發表的《粵港澳大灣區發展規劃綱要》中，已講明會「研究在澳門建立以人民幣計價結算的證券市場」，不過當時澳門當局聲稱，會以「發揮澳門所長，服務國家所需」為原則進行研究。<br />\n<br />\n而據內地媒體報道，澳門金管局正致力推動「中葡金融服務平台」的構建，及將內地工程機械﹑高鐵﹑造船等通過融資租賃公司，拓展至葡語國家及「一帶一路」沿線市場。似乎官方說法，是靠澳門連繫葡語國家的關係。<br />\n<br />\n不過，根據「葡萄牙語國家共同體」（CPLP）資料，全球使用葡語的人口僅得2.2億人，而經濟最大的國家是巴西及葡萄牙，其餘是東帝汶及其他非洲小國，是否有足夠資金買入中國龐大的基建債務，已成問題。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，澳門國際銀行及綠地已先後在澳門發行16.68億港元及2億美元債券，而非用葡萄牙流通貨幣歐元計價，反映其實澳門只是「掛羊頭賣狗肉」，直接與香港金融市場競爭。而隨著香港發生社會運動，內地早已不諱言讓澳門做香港的「Plan B」。<br />\n<br />\n既然澳門諗住搶香港生意，那麼香港是否應該重新討論賭場合法化？有澳門及新加坡的成功先例在前，香港大可以做澳門的「Plan B」，只要在機場及港珠澳大橋附近興建賭場，也可以取得大量賭收，解決龐大的社福及醫療需要，同時吸引大量商旅人士來港，令香港更國際化。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n不要跟我說要請示中央，《基本法》第16條講明，香港特別行政區享有行政管理權。香港要開賭場，中國及澳門其實都無權過問。不過以目前的低能傀儡政府，只會讓機會不斷流失，然後抱怨香港經濟不濟。<br />\n<br />\n我很想知道，澳門搞金融，香港開賭場，最後結果會係點？</span><br />\n<br />\n徐風<br />\n//<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n叫香港人呂志和大嶼山開賭場<br />\n<br />\n或者大嶼山搞碼頭，專開賭船出公海"},{"pid":"efcb3d757d65d715a474daee40f11272dcbf6fcb","tid":1789072,"uid":58552,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T07:47:27.000Z","msg":"Ok 換"},{"pid":"f4cb45953d432181c476db7e9ce120c46402831b","tid":1789072,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T07:47:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxvfDH.jpg&h=8ac82a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=d86Hk5Pgd4X%2FjIl3nTqvfMF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=d230c720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetower87</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tax87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftax87&d=d86Hk5Pgd4X%2FjIl3nTqvfMF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=e78fefef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tax87</a><br />\n<br />\n請推po<br />\n<br />\n【核彈】呢個方法可以防水炮車【行動po求推】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1778898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1778898</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9bda2e2d6b9dbf18aee811d316f62e10d7a3f379","tid":1789072,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T07:48:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4caa3b0fe3b0f9af2f87ce807340dc8d7820c033","tid":1789072,"uid":13138,"like":194,"dislike":1,"score":193,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T08:08:47.000Z","msg":"香港開放賭業，應該直接整死澳門<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n地方乾淨過澳門，仲有其他野玩/買野食野都方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />澳門仲邊有人去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca3f5509c8b4c72cab56320f9b6f6951cfbe80fb","tid":1789072,"uid":50526,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T08:14:47.000Z","msg":"已經有麗星雙魚星號，半架賭船嚟<br />\n支那封殺之下架船少咗好多客<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17b2b1d1673f7c0d0b9ea773b9e410efe0f93257","tid":1789072,"uid":172668,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T08:20:48.000Z","msg":"日本都開賭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港都可以開啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f25bc4836c567d8d907c200c31b2190f4ee55a4","tid":1789072,"uid":39855,"like":96,"dislike":1,"score":95,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T08:21:15.000Z","msg":"自從傳出澳門攪金融之後，似乎個個都醒起香港可以攪賭場。"},{"pid":"7ca4c5bd7f06c528beb2ef568c82ecfc54222f35","tid":1789072,"uid":78383,"like":49,"dislike":8,"score":41,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T08:21:46.000Z","msg":"搞賭係7傷拳黎嫁大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"241bd0065c88062fc238b302b81d9a6591f4863c","tid":1789072,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca3f5509c8b4c72cab56320f9b6f6951cfbe80fb","tid":1789072,"uid":50526,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T08:14:47.000Z","msg":"已經有麗星雙魚星號，半架賭船嚟<br />\n支那封殺之下架船少咗好多客<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T08:23:43.000Z","msg":"支那點封殺麗星雙魚星號？"},{"pid":"fdde65af5540d71407aa728cc25868560bce8756","tid":1789072,"uid":143151,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T08:24:54.000Z","msg":"開放賭牌 俾啲酒店改成賭場<br />\n<br />\n慳位慳力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84d7b3bfeb67a16a48ce8318712c6fba64fccdd0","tid":1789072,"uid":9116,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"quote":{"pid":"fdde65af5540d71407aa728cc25868560bce8756","tid":1789072,"uid":143151,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T08:24:54.000Z","msg":"開放賭牌 俾啲酒店改成賭場<br />\n<br />\n慳位慳力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T08:26:57.000Z","msg":"馬會第一個出嚟反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24a62629adb11553806c0b491788b818affa8bbb","tid":1789072,"uid":194869,"like":70,"dislike":1,"score":69,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T08:31:07.000Z","msg":"香港最大賭埸 港交所<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9b3c126b2748c319e22758ce7ce0003ef986724","tid":1789072,"ui